{"tid":346799,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS/AN] Kairosoft賽車物語2 育成賽車遊戲","createTime":"2017-08-04T09:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T10:24:32.000Z","uid":9699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a94c062c91ae9d64fc9d51dc01ed895347b6fc25","tid":346799,"uid":9699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T09:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.fengimg.com/data/attachment/forum/201707/06/143453v6bbxziiokb68ovo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fengimg.com%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201707%2F06%2F143453v6bbxziiokb68ovo.png&h=f2afee53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>遊戲名稱: </strong>[/size=2]</span><br />\n衝刺！賽車物語2 / Grand Prix Story 2<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">[size=4]遊戲簡介: </span></span></strong><br />\n玩家要負責賽車車隊的經營，並訓練你的駕駛員、培育技師，藉由相輔相成的系統，打造出最強的車隊，朝向 F1 那般的世界頂尖邁進。而且，經營車隊，隊中車手、賽車都不能馬虎，玩家除了可以選擇喜歡的車種進行開發之外，也可以選擇不同車手及技師加以培養以設計出獨一無二的機械。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>遊戲截圖: </strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Grand-Prix-Story2-1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2FGrand-Prix-Story2-1.jpeg&h=bbe4c9af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Grand-Prix-Story2-3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2FGrand-Prix-Story2-3.jpeg&h=9512e129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">下載地址:</span></span></strong><br />\nIOS: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/%E5%86%B2%E5%88%BA-%E8%B5%9B%E8%BD%A6%E7%89%A9%E8%AF%AD2/id1254318508?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2F%25E5%2586%25B2%25E5%2588%25BA-%25E8%25B5%259B%25E8%25BD%25A6%25E7%2589%25A9%25E8%25AF%25AD2%2Fid1254318508%3Fmt%3D8&d=rR2gLQwBRv6q9Yu%2B0eW34JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=e9d34fa4\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/%E5%86%B2%E5%88%BA-%E8%B5%9B%E8%BD%A6%E7%89%A9%E8%AF%AD2/id1254318508?mt=8</a><br />\nAN: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.kairosoft.android.paddock2_en&amp;hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dnet.kairosoft.android.paddock2_en%26hl%3Dzh-TW&d=rR2gLQwBRv6q9Yu%2B0eW34JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=ffbef776\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.kairosoft.android.paddock2_en&amp;hl=zh-TW</a></div><br />\n<br />\n鑑於之前個post內容比較貧乏,所以整個新post方便討論同參考玩法<br />\n順便新post吸引多d新玩家加入,始終隻game耐玩性都算高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee19d94c837ca7b0a7ac9c84d24351264a78aead","tid":346799,"uid":36087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T09:38:58.000Z","msg":"呢個係免費版本？"},{"pid":"20c7ad00e2dc4a704b0e0ad1fc492ba8e2df7828","tid":346799,"uid":9699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T09:46:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">攻略區</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊戲內各種車種數值及特性表: <br />\n<a href=\"https://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=3652303\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhome.gamer.com.tw%2FcreationDetail.php%3Fsn%3D3652303&d=rR2gLQwBRv6q9Yu%2B0eW34JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=b277feb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=3652303</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=3652342\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhome.gamer.com.tw%2FcreationDetail.php%3Fsn%3D3652342&d=rR2gLQwBRv6q9Yu%2B0eW34JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=4078bca3\" target=\"_blank\">https://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=3652342</a><br />\n<br />\n賽車技能表:<br />\n<a href=\"https://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=3653022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhome.gamer.com.tw%2FcreationDetail.php%3Fsn%3D3653022&d=rR2gLQwBRv6q9Yu%2B0eW34JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=02c20afe\" target=\"_blank\">https://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=3653022</a><br />\n<br />\n車手及技師技能表<br />\n<a href=\"https://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=3651873\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhome.gamer.com.tw%2FcreationDetail.php%3Fsn%3D3651873&d=rR2gLQwBRv6q9Yu%2B0eW34JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=40272adc\" target=\"_blank\">https://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=3651873</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣資深玩家既開局到中期心得/車手及技師推薦<br />\n<a href=\"https://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=3658809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhome.gamer.com.tw%2FcreationDetail.php%3Fsn%3D3658809&d=rR2gLQwBRv6q9Yu%2B0eW34JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=9f3d4e17\" target=\"_blank\">https://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=3658809</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓主個人心得</span></strong></span><br />\n1. 開局我幾認同上面台灣玩家個講法,用科學家做主角,因為滿1格就有100研究資料,e舊野寧濫勿缺,升車性能又好,升人物特性又好,總之真心有用過其他角色<br />\n(我係海盜開局,去到3格著黃光都無咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n2. 起手到而家我都用GT車, 越野車初期有用,中後期對我黎講已經無用,一架gt車搭AWD特性就可以通關成隻遊戲 (不過我都見有唔少老手雙修兩種車/用卡丁搭越野,所有方法都可以)<br />\n<br />\n3. 唔建議抽零件抽車,雖然都係考你眼界準唔準,但其實用商店買到果d零件升都夠用有突,至於車就更加唔洗,勁車耗油量高,而且仲要睇你技師既特性同數值,新車設計建議既數值,唔夠高既話,整到勁車出黎都可以比起初GT車屌打<br />\n<br />\n4. 個人建議買建築,唔課金玩一星期多少少已經有2400買2個江戶城,升爆左要彩蛋有彩蛋,整勁車時要勁車有勁車 (將風洞/試驗場擺係江戶城附近)<br />\n<br />\n5. 新手開頭好缺錢,我自己有個方法賺錢,遊戲入面你可以挑戰其他玩家,而你會有個星數,個個起手星數都係500,我維持係800以上時,會不過reload去搵d 獎勵有250萬既賽事,就算跑最尾都有25萬 (試過一次尾2,咁就賺50萬), 25萬錢對於前中期升建築都有好用,而家250萬/218萬既賽事,可以比到你隻車手同技師好多exp,同埋更快max到觀眾去拎香蕉做研究<br />\n<br />\n6. 建築升級永遠儲油庫優先,因為愈多油意味你打得愈多場,去到打大獎賽要連續咁打,缺油同棄權無分別, 如果打打下發現唔夠油,拎架低耗油/廢車去打限時任務既高級任務打到升lvl,升lvl會送滿油比你,我都係靠咁樣打大獎賽<br />\n<br />\n7. 研究院一定要研究尾翼同suspension,唔研究商店無得買,e2舊野好重要,幫你高速入彎<br />\n<br />\n8. 有幾多好友加幾多好友吧, 加好友時會有寶珠,可以加成高速/加速/入彎/環境"},{"pid":"be623991589655a12953d84e2f63b8224223e6c5","tid":346799,"uid":9699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T09:46:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個係免費版本？</blockquote><br />\n係"},{"pid":"791422078bb6d5f8ba0eaf093f9ac7bd83315cf0","tid":346799,"uid":9699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T09:51:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有興趣既話大家可以加我好友,應該會有兩粒寶珠加成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nID係142337264</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><br />\n新手有咩唔識隨便問(不過攻略區同個人心得應該解答哂架啦),老手都歡迎入黎一齊討論下點通關點整勁車,咩車搭咩配置打咩賽道..etc<br />\n唔好見怪,雖然之前已經有post簡介隻驚,但果個post變左留id同講自己抽d咩車多,變左玩抽野驚多過遊戲驚, 玩法討論少,所以開個新post重新黎過</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6556501dc88ad0d5d493838645d8aac8245c4dc3","tid":346799,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T09:55:59.000Z","msg":"可唔可以同其他玩家架車比賽？<br />\n隻game多唔多同人互動？"},{"pid":"2d5b385aa2109a11caa0991078a94015a34c03dc","tid":346799,"uid":9699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T09:59:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以同其他玩家架車比賽？<br />\n隻game多唔多同人互動？</blockquote><br />\n唔係即時對戰,即係果個玩家車庫用緊咩車,你就會隨機係挑戰list撞到佢<br />\n同埋基本上你一堆車比你挑戰,搵唔岩對手,返回再禁返「比賽」就會更新左個對手list,試過撞到巴打d車,但知道唔夠揪就無去玩"},{"pid":"27281bc9a61ffcfb2fc2c1d8ac4b4284bc033c56","tid":346799,"uid":9699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24577e2b1e938e4a3b8a8f42023a846509738729","tid":346799,"uid":9699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04